a.title: Spring Break Alert
a.span: Community Health Update Letter for Spring Break 2020 Travel

p.strong:
Until Further Notice
Vista Virtual School is OPEN

p.span: On Thursday, March 26th, the VUSD Board received an update on the state of the COVID-19 emergency worldwide and locally. Based upon this information, the Board determined that it was in the best interests of our students and our community to close all school with reopening pending positive health and safety reports from the state and county authorities.

br.span: Click HERE to view a PDF version of the presentation from their meeting or click the video below to see and hear a narrated version of the presentation.
